<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chess Coaching - Queen's Chess Club</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Vollkorn:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=League+Spartan:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.1/css/all.min.css">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="images/logo.jpg"/>
</head>

<%- include('header.ejs') %>

<body>
    <div class="centerer">
        <div class="width-container">
            <h1>FREE CHESS COACHING</h1>
            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 1.3rem;">
                Join our 12-week program. Drop in anytime: no sign-ups required!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="coaching-info-panel">
            <div class="coaching-info-item">
                <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                <div class="coaching-info-content">
                    <h3>Program Duration</h3>
                    <p>January 14th - April 1st, 2025</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="coaching-info-item">
                <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                <div class="coaching-info-content">
                    <h3>Schedule</h3>
                    <p>Every Wednesday, 6:00 PM - 7:00 PM</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="coaching-info-item">
                <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                <div class="coaching-info-content">
                    <h3>Location</h3>
                    <p>Kingston Hall Room 205</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="coaching-info-item">
                <i class="fas fa-gift"></i>
                <div class="coaching-info-content">
                    <h3>Cost</h3>
                    <p>Completely Free!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="width-container">
            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
                This program is completely free and will be occurring on a drop-in basis, meaning that no sign-ups are required. 
                Stop by to learn some exciting new chess skills and stay for the general meeting to test out your skills afterward!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="coaching-schedule-container">
            <h2>Program Schedule</h2>
            <div class="coaching-schedule-grid">
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">JAN 14</div>
                    <h3>Chess Thinking</h3>
                    <p>How do strong players think?</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">JAN 21</div>
                    <h3>Meet the Philosophers</h3>
                    <p>Core concepts of old-school masters</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">JAN 28</div>
                    <h3>Opening Principles</h3>
                    <p>Play the opening for the middlegame</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">FEB 4</div>
                    <h3>Prophylactic Thinking</h3>
                    <p>Stopping your opponent's attack</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">FEB 11</div>
                    <h3>Practical Openings</h3>
                    <p>Build your opening repertoire!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">FEB 18</div>
                    <h3>Piece Activity & Coordination</h3>
                    <p>Use your pieces strategically (TAKE HOME)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">FEB 25</div>
                    <h3>Chess Strategy</h3>
                    <p>Common opening mistakes</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">MAR 4</div>
                    <h3>Dynamic Imbalances</h3>
                    <p>When activity outweighs material</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">MAR 11</div>
                    <h3>Game Changer (Alphazero)</h3>
                    <p>Modern ideas in chess</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">MAR 18</div>
                    <h3>Attack</h3>
                    <p>Mastering the unsound attacks vs missed attacking chances</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">MAR 25</div>
                    <h3>Attack</h3>
                    <p>Structured attacks, not "hope chess"!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="coaching-session-card">
                    <div class="session-date">APR 1</div>
                    <h3>Middlegame to Endgame</h3>
                    <p>Transitions</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="coaching-cta">
            <h2>Interested in the Coaching Program?</h2>
            <p>Let us know what you'd like to see by filling out this form:</p>
            <a href="https://forms.gle/oVi4WKSwnRvAxiAm7" target="_blank" class="coaching-form-button">
                <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i> Fill Out the Form
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('footer.ejs'); %>

</body>
</html>
